children.subject: Whats it going to be about ? (sorry , its my first sem here)

history.content:
A quick reminder that the academic intern orientation for those AI-ing for EECS department classes (CS10, CS61A, CS61B, CS61C, CS88, DATA8, DATA100) will be tomorrow (9/6) 4-5PM in Sibley Auditorium. 

Unless you have an unavoidable conflict, we look forward to seeing everyone there! Slides will be posted afterwards here for those who can’t make it. 

EDIT: Slides here https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1uzNUafKAaFEkAWo-ijuSah-oReg1Caf0zZwveyp3LRA
